WFSVideo Demo

JavaScript plugin

javascript plugin for your website or mobile application

The plugin is designed to view videos in a modal window.

Plugin benefits:

  • Plugin weight - javascript/css - 15,9 KB
  • Easy to customize.
  • Lots of settings.
  • 4 types of video insertion ("video", "youtube", "vimeo", "tiktok").
  • Detailed instructions.
  • Plugin launch prompts in console.log()
